value.name: FUBAR
value.overview: When a father and daughter discover they both secretly work for the CIA, an already dicey undercover mission turns into a dysfunctional family affair.

value.name: Fubar Age of Computer
value.overview: Fleeing the wildfires of Fort McMurray, Terry and Dean retreat to Terry's cousin Shank's illegal basement suite in Calgary, where Terry discovers high speed Internet and Dean embarks on an epic journey to record his concept album, '3069.'
